---
title: Double Herby Chicken & Cheddar Crushed Potatoes with Dijon Avocado Slaw
description: Mustard, cheese and herbs, they are the magical ingredients we’ve added to conjure a dish like no other, worthy of
your tastebuds. Watch as the cheese is melted over crushed potatoes, and the Dijon in the slaw is the hidden gem we
love for a herby chicken dinner.
